{
  "text": "We propose a DUPMN model. Firstly, document representation is learned by a hierarchical LSTM network to obtain both sentence-level representation and document level representation [CITATION_1] . A memory network model is then trained using dual memory networks, one for training user profiles and the other for training product reviews. Both of them are joined together to predict sentiment for documents.",
